title: WPScan
extract: WPScan is a black box WordPress vulnerability scanner that can be used to scan remote WordPress installations to find security issues. Source: http://wpscan.org/ WPScan Homepage | Kali wpscan Repo. Author: The WPScan Team.Feb 18, 2014
